text: Cristóbal Grez (born 17 December 1987) is a Chilean competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's 49er. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Cristobal Category:Chilean male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Chile Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 49er Category:Pan American Games medalists in sailing Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Chile Category:Sailors at the 2011 Pan American Games
